      <title>南非在打击犯罪方面取得一定成效</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/south-africa-showcases-some-success-in-fighting-crime-scourge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非警察局长表示，执法机构在打击南非犯罪祸害方面取得了重大进展，捣毁了一批犯罪团伙，缴获了数千件非法武器和大量毒品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/south-africa-showcases-some-success-in-fighting-crime-scourge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 10:43:10 GMT</pubDate>
