    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚获得 200 亿美元资金，准备应对价格冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/ethiopia-birr-reforms-unlock-20-billion-of-funding-threaten-price-shock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃塞俄比亚本周决定让本币浮动，从而获得了世界银行和国际货币基金组织超过 200 亿美元的融资，而这个东非国家的政府急需这笔资金来缓解其债务负担并开放经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/ethiopia-birr-reforms-unlock-20-billion-of-funding-threaten-price-shock</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 09:24:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称已确认哈马斯二号人物戴夫被击毙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/israel-says-it-s-confirmed-hamas-number-two-deif-was-killed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列称，已证实哈马斯军事首脑穆罕默德·戴夫在上个月对加沙的一次袭击中身亡。此前一天，哈马斯政治领袖伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚在德黑兰遇害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/israel-says-it-s-confirmed-hamas-number-two-deif-was-killed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 08:36:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国承诺加大对农民工的支持以提振需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/china-vows-to-lend-more-support-to-rural-migrants-in-demand-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国承诺为从农村进城务工人员提供更好的公共服务，此举将消除城镇化的障碍并促进经济发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/china-vows-to-lend-more-support-to-rural-migrants-in-demand-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:20:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管暗杀事件受挫，美国仍推动加沙停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/biden-team-still-pushing-gaza-cease-fire-after-israel-s-strikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉拜登政府想法的人士透露，美国官员仍在推动加沙停火，但承认在以色列疑似袭击导致哈马斯高级领导人在德黑兰死亡后，停火比以往任何时候都更加困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/biden-team-still-pushing-gaza-cease-fire-after-israel-s-strikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 14:17:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
